<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Hadamard-Code.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Hadamard-Code.svg/250px-Hadamard-Code.svg.png" width="250" height="500" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Hadamard-Code.svg/375px-Hadamard-Code.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Hadamard-Code.svg/500px-Hadamard-Code.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="32" data-file-height="64" /></a>
