Matrix of the Hadamard code (32, 6, 16) for the <a href="/wiki/Reed-Muller_Code" title="Reed-Muller Code" class="mw-redirect">Reed-Muller Code</a> (1, 5) of the NASA space probe <a href="/wiki/Mariner_9" title="Mariner 9">Mariner 9</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Multigrade_operator_XOR.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1e/Multigrade_operator_XOR.svg/250px-Multigrade_operator_XOR.svg.png" width="250" height="202" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1e/Multigrade_operator_XOR.svg/375px-Multigrade_operator_XOR.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1e/Multigrade_operator_XOR.svg/500px-Multigrade_operator_XOR.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="361" data-file-height="291" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Multigrade_operator_XOR.svg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>
<a href="/wiki/Exclusive_or" title="Exclusive or">XOR</a> operations<br />
